{"tid":220764,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"被誤認車迷 熱刺支持者遭「自己人」痛毆","createTime":"2017-04-28T07:59:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-28T10:25:42.000Z","uid":38189,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"68edf9fb38b69bd0c9fd68bb40122bcac5711260","tid":220764,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T07:59:46.000Z","msg":"一名熱刺球迷在上周足總盃四強賽後遭毆打至重傷，消息指他因被其他熱刺球迷誤認為車路士「粉絲」而惹禍，事件亦獲當地警方高度關注。<br />\n<br />\n事件受害人Michael Voller為熱刺球迷，據指他在一間餐廳外與一批熱刺球迷迎面而過，惟卻被對方誤當為對手車路士的球迷，結果被毆打至重傷，他面部有骨折，眼部亦有傷，事後需要送院，而醫生指其視力可能會受永久性損傷。<br />\n<br />\n當地警方表示高度關注事件，又呼籲知情的熱刺球迷勸涉案人事自首：「這種暴力行為在足球界是絕不容發生的。我希望知情人事盡快提供消息，還這名自小便是熱刺球迷的年輕人一個公道。」（<a href=\"http://Goal.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FGoal.com&d=U3in%2BbByR8w%2FZmejrHnAdTPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=b89512fd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Goal.com</a>）<br />\n<br />\n收到風牛口非黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44420234806db7b2bdf1d857a0671031956bc4a0","tid":220764,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T08:17:00.000Z","msg":"熱犬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab842ae6bcf50d14dc36e15b64e869ee59c55330","tid":220764,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T08:30:23.000Z","msg":"波台好靜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0a0e8d9f4cb91587b190d34c46801c2299187d3","tid":220764,"uid":22589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T08:32:51.000Z","msg":"往死裏打"},{"pid":"d599e4ee03c25fdd759ef4294d5966782c034da4","tid":220764,"uid":107590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T08:33:04.000Z","msg":"隊波個個都好抽得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f82236c91b51f1fee3fe61803bad9a694c2cf310","tid":220764,"uid":12034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T08:33:40.000Z","msg":"<blo